  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 + Griffel `makeStyles` + semantic tokens mandatory; no v8 components, no inline styles</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Shared Kanban components MUST live in `@spaarke/smart-todo-components` peer package — NOT duplicated between widget and app</constraint>
    <constraint source="No regression">Code Page's existing Kanban behavior MUST be preserved bit-for-bit after the hoist (drag, drop, pin, multi-select, card render). Consumer change is import-source swap only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="React 19">Peer package is React 19 + Vite Code Page consumers. react-dnd v16+ supports React 19; use that version.</constraint>
    <constraint source="Pin persistence">Pin state persists to the existing `sprk_todo` Dataverse field (likely `sprk_pinned` boolean — verify in Code Page source); the hoist must preserve this Xrm.WebApi write path</constraint>
    <constraint source="Multi-select model">Selection is `Set&lt;string&gt;` (matches app's pattern at SmartTodoLayout:~121); R4-099's single `selectedId` in widget becomes `selectedIds: Set&lt;string&gt;`</constraint>
    <constraint source="durable user instruction">spaarkedev1 deploys are master-only; do NOT propose a branch deploy</constraint>
  </constraints>

