    </related-work>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context check">Confirm context &lt; 70%. Read the audit-findings note.</step>
    <step order="1" name="Read app Kanban source">Read SmartToDo.tsx + KanbanCard.tsx end-to-end. Map out: column rendering, drag-drop handlers, pin handler, multi-select handler, card tool icons (Open + Pin + others), state lift points.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Read existing shared-lib Kanban">Read `Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/Kanban/KanbanBoard.tsx` (R4-070). Decide: extend in-place vs. create domain-specific composer in `@spaarke/smart-todo-components`. Default decision per knowledge pattern: keep visual primitive in `@spaarke/ui-components` (generic), put SmartTodo-specific composition (with TodoData domain types + Xrm.WebApi pin writer + drag→column-mutation handlers) in `@spaarke/smart-todo-components`.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Add react-dnd workspace dep">Update `src/client/shared/Spaarke.SmartTodo.Components/package.json` to add `"react-dnd": "^16.0.0"` + `"react-dnd-html5-backend": "^16.0.0"` (or matching versions used in app). Run npm install. Verify install works without peer-dep blowback.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Hoist KanbanCard">Move KanbanCard.tsx from `src/solutions/SmartTodo/src/components/` into `src/client/shared/Spaarke.SmartTodo.Components/src/components/KanbanCard/` (with index.ts + styles split). Card preserves: select checkbox + tool icons (Open invokes onOpenTodo via dispatch; Pin invokes onPinToggle which writes to sprk_todo via injected webApi). Domain types come from peer package's existing types module.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Build SmartTodoKanban container in peer package">Create `src/client/shared/Spaarke.SmartTodo.Components/src/components/SmartTodoKanban/` (KanbanColumns container + DragDropProvider wrapper + state hooks). Consumes `useKanbanColumns` (already hoisted) + `KanbanCard` (just hoisted). Exposes `<SmartTodoKanban items={...} selectedIds={...} onSelectionChange={...} onOpenTodo={...} onPinToggle={...} webApi={...} orientation="horizontal"|"vertical" />`. Drag-drop persists column changes via injected webApi.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Swap Code Page consumer">Update `src/solutions/SmartTodo/src/components/SmartToDo.tsx` to import + render `<SmartTodoKanban>` from peer package. Delete local KanbanCard.tsx. Verify Code Page Kanban renders + drag-drop + pin + multi-select all work bit-for-bit as before.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Swap widget consumer">Update `SmartTodoWidget.tsx` to render `<SmartTodoKanban>` instead of R4-101's grouped lists. Wire orientation toggle (UAT item 3) via new toolbar control. Wire multi-select via `selectedIds: Set&lt;string&gt;` state (replacing R4-099's single `selectedId`). Pass webApi + Xrm-derived callbacks. Verify widget renders the full Kanban + drag-drop + pin + multi-select all work.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Build verify">`npm run build` (tsc) in `@spaarke/smart-todo-components` + `npm run build` (Vite) in SmartTodo + LegalWorkspace + SpaarkeAi. All four must build green.</step>
    <step order="9" name="Quality gates">Run `code-review` + `adr-check` on modified files per task-execute Step 9.5. ADR-012 + ADR-021 are binding.</step>
    <step order="10" name="Update task status">Flip POML status to `complete`. Update TASK-INDEX.md row + header counts. Note closeout of R4-020 deferred 13-file subtree.</step>
  </steps>

