  <notes>
## Completion Notes — R4-102 (E-1) Widget Kanban hoist (2026-06-18)

### Architecture decision (mirrors Calendar pattern)

Generic visual primitive `KanbanBoard` (drag-drop infrastructure + `orientation` prop) stays in `@spaarke/ui-components` (already there from R3-010 + R4-070). SmartTodo-domain composition lives in `@spaarke/smart-todo-components`:

- `components/KanbanCard/` — sprk_todo-shaped card (hoisted from app's `src/solutions/SmartTodo/src/components/KanbanCard.tsx`, bit-for-bit visual + interaction parity).
- `components/SmartTodoKanban/` — domain composer that wraps `<KanbanBoard>` + `useKanbanColumns` + `<KanbanCard>`, providing the drag-end handler (`COLUMN_ID_MAP` map + `moveItem`/`reorderInColumn`), pin handler, multi-select / open wiring.
- `utils/todoScoring.ts` — shared score + due-label helpers (copies from app's `todoScoreUtils.ts` / `dueLabelUtils.ts`, kept self-contained per the established `useKanbanColumns` precedent — peer package is host-agnostic).

### DnD library

POML referenced `react-dnd` but the actual library in use across all 4 consumer code pages is **`@hello-pangea/dnd`** (a fork of react-beautiful-dnd). Added as `^17.0.0 || ^18.0.0` peerDep + `^18.0.1` devDep on the peer package. No new transitive cost — all consumers already had it.

### Files created (9)

- `src/components/KanbanCard/KanbanCard.tsx` (368 LOC) — hoisted domain card
- `src/components/KanbanCard/KanbanCard.styles.ts` (122 LOC) — Griffel styles (copy)
- `src/components/KanbanCard/index.ts` — barrel
- `src/components/SmartTodoKanban/SmartTodoKanban.tsx` (197 LOC) — domain composer
- `src/components/SmartTodoKanban/index.ts` — barrel
- `src/components/index.ts` — components barrel re-export
- `src/utils/todoScoring.ts` (143 LOC) — shared scoring helpers

### Files modified (9)

- `package.json` — added `@hello-pangea/dnd` peerDep + devDep, exposed `./components` exports subpath
- `src/index.ts` — added `export * from './components'`
- `src/types/index.ts` — re-exported `IKanbanCardTodo` + `KanbanOrientation`
- `src/types/kanban.ts` — added `IKanbanCardTodo` superset, re-exported `KanbanOrientation`
- `src/types/todo.ts` — added optional `updateRecord` to `IWebApi` for widget persistence
- `src/widgets/SmartTodoWidget/SmartTodoWidget.tsx` — replaced grouped lists with `<SmartTodoKanban>`; selection model upgraded from `string|null` → `Set<string>`; added `<OrientationToggle>` + local `orientation` state; built `dataverseService` adapter wrapping `webApi.updateRecord` for drag-drop + pin persistence
- `src/widgets/SmartTodoWidget/SmartTodoWidget.styles.ts` — added `kanbanContainer` style (R4-101 group* styles left intact, unused — follow-up cleanup)
- `src/solutions/SmartTodo/src/components/SmartToDo.tsx` — swapped `KanbanCard` import from `./KanbanCard` → `@spaarke/smart-todo-components`; R4-104's QuickAdd wiring preserved bit-for-bit
- `src/solutions/SmartTodo/src/components/index.ts` — barrel re-export from peer package
- `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/vite.config.ts` — added `@spaarke/sdap-client` workaround alias (7th surface; pre-existing PR #369 cascade — broke on master before this task too, not introduced here)

### Files deleted (1)

- `src/solutions/SmartTodo/src/components/KanbanCard.tsx` (565 LOC) — fully hoisted into peer package

